nodes.text: Fan Faire 2009 Commemorative Painting was a painting made during the Galactic Civil War. It had Princess Leia, Darth Vader, Han Solo, Jango Fett, Luke Skywalker, the Death Star, Chewbacca, C-3PO, R2-D2 and Warren Wicket on it, as well as the words "Galactic Gathering 2009."
It was given out to the players who attended the summit in 2009. It is flagged as a no trade item.
